                              "name": "notePara2",
                              "fill": "#9CA3AF",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "Multi-head attention runs the mechanism h times in parallel, allowing the model to jointly attend to information from different representation subspaces.",
